summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of the portion of Lots 2, 3 and the west 40 feet of Lot 4, Block 39, Woodland Addition to Salmon Bay City, lying southerly of Green Lake Way as established by Ordinance No. 59719, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-143 and 17-104, respectively.
